text: This was the first edition of the tournament. Julian Knowle and Igor Zelenay won the title after defeating Rameez Junaid and Kevin Krawietz 2–6, 6–2, [10–7] in the final. ==Seeds== ==Draw== ==References== * Main Draw Internazionali di Tennis d'Abruzzo - Doubles
